## Installation

For development:

```bash
pip install -e "packages/{{ pkg_name }}[dev]"
```

## Running the API

### Development

```bash
cd packages/{{ pkg_name }}
uvicorn {{ pkg_name }}.main:app --reload --port {{ api_port }}
```

### Production with Docker

```bash
cd packages/{{ pkg_name }}
docker build -t {{ pkg_name }} .
docker run -p {{ api_port }}:{{ api_port }} {{ pkg_name }}
```

## API Documentation

